Ing '''Bouyon''' metung yang village at [[commune in France|commune]] king  [[Alpes-Maritimes]] ''[[départements of France|département]]'' ning [[France]].

Atiu mga 30 km king pangulungalbugan ning [[Nice]], Bouyon atin yang mangasanting a pialben king bunduk ning  [[Alps]], at ding kayang pangkaugalian a [[château]] at communal bread oven. Ding Local leisure a gagawan da reng tau karin ilapin ding manukyat bunduk, magbisikleta keng bunduk, tennis, at manasan at ating yang banu-banuang [[kapagmasusian]] o ausan dang [[party|Fête]] in June and August.

